        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "希有！",
        "from": "T07n0220_582:1011c09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "善逝！",
        "from": "T07n0220_582:1011c09_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "成就如是大威神力，能令我等得見東方無量殑伽沙等世界，無數菩薩摩訶薩眾行菩薩行種種差別，無數如來、應、正等覺種種方便饒益有情。",
        "from": "T07n0220_582:1011c09_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "甚奇！",
        "from": "T07n0220_582:1011c13_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
